Today had Intravesical Botox as she has failed myrbetriq, vesicare.
S/p Intravesical Botox, improved, appears to have UTI, will treat with macrobid, will follow up in 6 months.
Telephon / video visit: She did not wish to repeat Intravesical Botox. Counseled on all options and will try PTNS.
